          "hint": {
            "en": "Select actions controlled by input 2 on the device. \n\nNOTE 1: If the \"Dual\" option is selected for input 1, the selection for input 2 will have no effect. No Flow cards named \"Input 2\" will be triggered. For devices with two outputs, output 2 will not be controlled by input 2.\n\nNOTE 2: If a \"Scene selector\" option is selected, the input will not control the output and no Flow cards will be triggered.\n\nNOTE 3: For the \"Stationary switch as selector\", the primary scene is recalled in \"On\" state and the secondary scene is recalled in \"Off\" state. For the \"Momentary switch as selector\", the primary scene is recalled with short-click and the secondary scene is recalled with long-click."
